@startuml
title State Machine: Incident Lifecycle

[*] --> Reported
Reported : Call received\nIncident created

Reported --> Verified : Validate details
Verified : Location confirmed\nPriority assigned

Verified --> Dispatched : Units assigned
Dispatched : Officers notified\nEn route

Dispatched --> Responding : Units responding
Responding : On scene arrival\nIn progress

Responding --> Investigating : Scene processing
Investigating : Evidence collection\nWitness interviews

Investigating --> Resolved : Immediate resolution
Resolved : Initial handling complete

Resolved --> Documenting : Report writing
Documenting : Official reports\nDocumentation

Documenting --> Closed : All reports filed
Closed : Incident closed\nNo further action

Resolved --> CaseGenerated : Requires follow-up
CaseGenerated --> [*] : New case created

Closed --> [*]
@enduml
